616
00:40:22,486 --> 00:40:25,284
No la necesito para probar su culpabilidad.

617
00:40:27,157 --> 00:40:29,125
Dime una cosa.

618
00:40:29,159 --> 00:40:31,787
¿Te molesta que te llame Willy?

619
00:40:31,829 --> 00:40:34,024
No.

620
00:40:34,164 --> 00:40:36,464
No.

621
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,694
Willy.

622
00:40:41,004 --> 00:40:44,337
Willy, quiero que consideres
ser mi abogado.

623
00:40:46,343 --> 00:40:48,038
