754
00:46:43,333 --> 00:46:45,824
Sí, deseo objetar.

755
00:46:45,869 --> 00:46:47,336
¿Con qué bases?

756
00:46:47,370 --> 00:46:48,860
No sé.

757
00:46:48,905 --> 00:46:50,839
Su Señoría...

758
00:46:50,874 --> 00:46:54,674
